Yokkaichi.title: Yokkaichi
Yokkaichi.byline: Yokkaichi (四日市) is a city in Mie prefecture, Japan.

Yokohama.title: Yokohama
Yokohama.byline: On the western coast of Tokyo Bay directly south of Tokyo, Yokohama (横浜) is the second largest city in Japan and one of the cities most used to seeing foreigners.
